  "text": "Beside the official EDL bill, households and shops pay another bill to private generators at a largely higher cost of 45 US cents per kWh (Hamdan, Ghajar, and Chedid [CITATION_1] ). The large difference between private generator fees and EDL tariffs represents an additional constraint to personal consumption and thus to economic growth.",
